{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"includeOptional","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" = true) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Hashable","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"tag","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value to use as the view’s tag.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"includeOptional","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the tag value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<V>"},{"type":"text","text":" should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also be set."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view with the specified tag set."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to differentiate among certain selectable views,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"like the possible values of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"text":" or the tabs of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TabView"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Tag values can be of any type that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This modifier will write the tag value for the type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"V"},{"text":", as well as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<V>"},{"text":" if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"includeOptional"},{"text":" is enabled. Containers checking for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags of either type will see the value as set.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the example below, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach"},{"type":"text","text":" loop in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"builder iterates over the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Flavor"},{"type":"text","text":" enumeration. It extracts the string"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of each enumeration element for use in constructing the row"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"label, and uses the enumeration value as input to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"tag(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifier."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["struct FlavorPicker: View {","    enum Flavor: String, CaseIterable, Identifiable {","        case chocolate, vanilla, strawberry","        var id: Self { self }","    }","","    @State private var selectedFlavor: Flavor? = nil","","    var body: some View {","        Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","            ForEach(Flavor.allCases) { flavor in","                Text(flavor.rawValue)","                    .tag(flavor)","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The selection type of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<Flavor>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and so it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will look for tags on its contents of ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<Flavor>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"type. Since the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tag modifier defaults to having ","type":"text"},{"code":"includeOptional","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" enabled, even though","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the tag for each option is a non-optional ","type":"text"},{"code":"Flavor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the tag modifier","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"writes values for both the non-optional, and optional versions of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value, allowing the contents to be selectable by the ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" automatically applies a default tag to each enumerated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view using the "},{"code":"id","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter of the corresponding element. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the element’s "},{"code":"id","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter and the picker’s "},{"code":"selection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" input"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have exactly the same type, or the same type but optional, you can omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the explicit tag modifier."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To see examples that don’t require an explicit tag, see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EquatableView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EquatableView\/tag(_:includeOptional:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/equatableview\/tag(_:includeoptional:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"10.15"},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"6.0"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"title":"tag(_:includeOptional:)","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"tag"},{"kind":"text","